    N=4: terms=10/16 (62.5%), deg=4, max|c|=4, sub_rank=4, lower_bound>=4, time=0.0s
    N=5: terms=21/32 (65.6%), deg=4, max|c|=6, sub_rank=4, lower_bound>=4, time=0.0s
